text.section:
A guardian for a minor ward appointed prior to July 13, 1990, shall have the powers and duties:
Specified in KRS 387.135, if the guardian was appointed to have care, custody and control of a minor;
Specified in KRS 387.137, if the guardian was appointed to manage the financial resources of a minor;
Specified in KRS 387.065 and 387.125, if the guardian was appointed to have care, custody, and control of a minor and to manage the minor's financial resources.
